                    .company-address.lg-w-1-2.px-6 
                        h2.title-font.font-semibold.text-gray-900.tracking-widest.text-xs Address
                        p.mt-1 Lorem ipsum, dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Nam quasi nisi illum voluptate minus?
                    .company-email-phone.lg-w-1-2.px-6.mt-4.lg-mt-0
